munistd.h(7) Miscellaneous Information Manual munistd.h(7)

NAME

munistd.h — header wrapper

LIBRARY

library “libmjo”

SYNOPSIS

#include <munistd.h>

INCLUDES

<unistd.h>

DESCRIPTION

This module only includes the header file “unistd.h” when it is available. It does not define any of the routines, constants or symbols.

NOTES

Make the header more portable and compatible with OpenWatcom “unistd.h”

July 22, 2020 OpenBSD 7.0
